`,t.jsx(e.p,{children:"A Kubernetes Operator is a method of automating the management of complex applications on Kubernetes. It extends Kubernetes' capabilities by using custom resources and controllers to manage the lifecycle of an application, automating tasks such as deployment, scaling, and updates. Operators encode the operational knowledge of an application into Kubernetes, making it easier to manage stateful or complex workloads with less manual intervention."}),`
